Frána is hiding near the Mead Hall of Thornhope.\n\nYou should escort Frána to safety.
'You there! Help me escape this place... I demand it!\n\n'Wh-what? You say you cleared a path through the beasts? Well then, I will hurry to Béortnoth's camp.'
Frána is hiding near the Mead Hall of Thornhope.\n\nYou should escort Frána to safety.
Frána is at Béortnoth's camp, outside of Thornhope.\n\nYou should speak with Frána when you return to Béortnoth's camp.

'I suppose I should be grateful for your assistance, but you have delivered me into the hands of a madman! I shall not call Béortnoth Thane... not until he finds me a comfortable home in which to dwell.'
'I think I can make it from here!'
Talk to Frána at Béortnoth's camp
